  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958640/extras/525c7849ea326ce92476823621780839.avif?t=1647878124\" width=550 height=150 /></span><br><br><br>'Super Turbo Sudoku' is a classic Sudoku game with puzzles for beginners and pros.<br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>90 unique Sudokus<br></li><li>6 Difficulties: From \"Very Easy\" to \"Insane\"<br></li><li>Sudoku Solver: Enter your own Sudoku and get the solution<br></li><li>Level Editor: Create your own Sudokus<br></li><li>15 Achievements</li></ul><br>Lay back, take your shoes off and enter the exiting world of \"Super Turbo Sudoku\"!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/958640/extras/525c7849ea326ce92476823621780839.avif?t=1647878124\" width=550 height=150 /></span><br><br><br>'Super Turbo Sudoku' is a classic Sudoku game with puzzles for beginners and pros.<br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>90 unique Sudokus<br></li><li>6 Difficulties: From \"Very Easy\" to \"Insane\"<br></li><li>Sudoku Solver: Enter your own Sudoku and get the solution<br></li><li>Level Editor: Create your own Sudokus<br></li><li>15 Achievements</li></ul><br>Lay back, take your shoes off and enter the exiting world of \"Super Turbo Sudoku\"!",
